Firestrike was ready as Prowl came down the hole however.  He 
had quickly weakened the floor in front of him with a blast of his fire 
cannon.  "Come into my parlour I believe the phrase is" he said.  
The acid shots wizzed by him two hitting peieces of his armour and 
corroding small holes through it, and meltign a bit of his main body 
metals.  The weakened floor was right under Prowl.  "Boo." he said 
as oen hand grabbed the armour where it had been corroded and 
the other fired a blast of fire towards the ground, causing the floor 
to collapse.
